Entity.Types.description:
Describes different types of entities. Used by the Entity constructor 'type' param.

    Entity.Types = {
        zombie: {
           name: 'Zombie',
           char: 'z',
           color: 'red',
           bgColor: '#222'
        },
        // ...
    }

example:
//bindings param example:
{
    up: ['UP_ARROW'],
    down: ['DOWN_ARROW'],
    left: ['LEFT_ARROW'],
    right: ['RIGHT_ARROW'],
}

